					<div class="bio">
						<h4>Rachel Corbett</h4>
												<p>Rachel Corbett is the author of <em>You Must Change Your Life</em>, which won the Marfield Prize, the National Award for Arts Writing. She is a features writer at <em>New York</em> magazine, her writing has appeared in <em>The New Yorker</em>, <em>New York Times Magazine</em>, and <em>The Atlantic</em>. She lives in Brooklyn, New York.</p>
